name: Senior #4 - Coco
description:
Coco is a 68-year-old senior intern at a law firm who enjoys paid charity work, fashion and working on her meat pie recipe. She is kind and modest, but can also be very mellow and a bit pompous.

Coco's best friend is a customer service at a botox clinic called Shelby. They have a very firey friendship. She also hangs around with Ellen and Miko. All of them enjoy camping together.
